com.github.qacore.testingtoolbox.configuration

Class AdditionalProperties<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.qacore.testingtoolbox.configuration.AdditionalProperties<K,V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - The type of keys maintained by this map.
    V - The type of mapped values.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractWebDriverConfiguration, JavaTestingToolboxConfiguration, JUnitConfiguration, SeleniumConfiguration

    public class AdditionalProperties<K,V>
extends java.lang.Object
    Used by classes to indicate that they have additional properties. This can be used for run-time detection of features.
